* {{Cite web |last=Wilkes |first=Emma |date=December 17, 2022 |title=Miley Cyrus teases new music for 2023: "New Year, new Miley" |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-teases-new-music-for-2023-new-year-new-miley-3368323 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221230213135/https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-teases-new-music-for-2023-new-year-new-miley-3368323 |archive-date=December 30, 2022 |access-date=January 3, 2023 |website=[[NME]]}} 
