* {{Cite web |last=Henderson |first=Taylor |date=August 5, 2020 |title=Miley Cyrus Teases New Era of Music&nbsp;... With Dua Lipa |url=https://www.pride.com/music/2020/8/05/miley-cyrus-teases-new-era-musicwith-dua-lipa |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220922122730/https://www.pride.com/music/2020/8/05/miley-cyrus-teases-new-era-music-with-dua-lipa |archive-date=September 22, 2022 |access-date=September 22, 2022 |work=[[Pride.com]]}}</ref> She has also been considered a [[pop icon]] by several media outlets,<ref>* {{Cite news |last=Jiménez |first=Andrea |date=November 23, 2022 |title=Miley Cyrus at 30: From Disney child star to pop icon |url=https://english.elpais.com/culture/2022-11-23/miley-cyrus-at-30-from-disney-child-star-to-pop-icon.html |access-date=June 4, 2024 |work=[[El País]] }}
